Interface DisqueAsyncCommands<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - Key type.
    V - Value type.
    All Superinterfaces:

    public interface DisqueAsyncCommands<K,V>
extends DisqueJobAsyncCommands<K,V>, DisqueQueueAsyncCommands<K,V>, DisqueServerAsyncCommands<K,V>, DisqueClusterAsyncCommands<K,V>
    Asynchronous executed commands for Disque. This API is thread-safe.

    Mark Paluch
